00:18:23.829 --> 00:18:26.370
And throughout the day, there's
lots of opportunities for you

00:18:26.370 --> 00:18:28.786
to connect with developers--
really want to hear from you,

00:18:28.786 --> 00:18:31.170
hear what you care about.

00:18:31.170 --> 00:18:36.020
Because ultimately we want to
help make you all successful.

00:18:36.020 --> 00:18:40.970
So with that, I'm really
excited to see and learn

00:18:40.970 --> 00:18:44.347
what you guys can create
on top of the platform

00:18:44.347 --> 00:18:45.180
that we're building.

00:18:45.180 --> 00:18:47.620
So thank you so much
